user.biography:
Small family-owned toy shop. 
🍽 Every purchase helps provide meals for kids in need
📦 Flat-rate US shipping: $3.50
🌴 Based in Rancho Mission Viejo, CA

node.text: Pre-orders are now open for these music boxes! We’re expecting to receive our shipment by mid August, but shipping delays seem to be pretty common these days, so it could be later… Pre-orders will be open only this week! After that, these will be available to order once they arrive in our warehouse. 🧡
